One-year outcomes from a phase 3 randomized trial of ravulizumab in adults with 
paroxysmal nocturnal hemoglobinuria who received prior eculizumab.

Kulasekararaj AG(1), Hill A(2), Langemeijer S(3), Wells R(4), González Fernández 
FA(5), Gaya A(6), Ojeda Gutierrez E(7), Piatek CI(8), Mitchell L(9), Usuki 
K(10), Bosi A(11), Brodsky RA(12), Ogawa M(13), Yu J(13), Ortiz S(13), Röth 
